"""
google_agent/source/rag_retrieval_agent.py
===============================================================================
RagRetrievalAgent — rich dynamic source-truth retrieval for AI Live Tutor.

Purpose:
- Build a strong sourceTruthPacket for one selected node.
- Use real source text/chunks/pageContexts/selectedPageFullText only.
- Never invent source evidence.
- Expand thin selectedEvidence/sourceRefs into multiple grounded evidence cards.
- Preserve fullPdfSummary/fullPdfOutline/fullPdfOutlineText for downstream agents.
- Keep comparison/nearby pages separate so selected concept does not get polluted.

This agent is intentionally NOT ADK-first:
- RAG should be deterministic and faithful to source.
- Gemini/ADK can teach later, but RAG must provide truth.
===============================================================================
"""

